97
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:43,030
So good! I could eat a bucket full.

98
00:05:43,030 --> 00:05:44,860
Kariya...

99
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:46,970
Woo-hoo, the legend has it.

100
00:05:46,970 --> 00:05:49,280
Everyone, look this way!

101
