113
00:06:22,340 --> 00:06:24,770
Hashimoto?

114
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:42,970
Are you mad because I didn't notice this?

115
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:46,110
No.

116
00:06:46,770 --> 00:06:49,150
