196
00:10:56,540 --> 00:10:58,070
make me feel happy.

197
00:10:58,070 --> 00:10:59,910
Thank you, guys.

198
00:11:01,710 --> 00:11:04,080
To respect Aoki's passionate feelings toward you,

199
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:07,410
