219
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:48,650
About five minutes ago.

220
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:52,260
Aoki, your cake was so good.

221
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:54,250
- Good to hear.
- Thanks.

222
00:12:58,270 --> 00:13:00,350
Aoki!

223
00:13:01,070 --> 00:13:03,330
Hashimoto.

224
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:06,010
Did it go well with Akkun?

225
00:13:06,010 --> 00:13:07,640
Yes.

226
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,040
Aida said,

227
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:14,010
