228
00:13:14,010 --> 00:13:16,200
I see.

229
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,060
I'm so glad!

230
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:19,950
It's all thanks to you, Aoki.

231
00:13:19,950 --> 00:13:22,820
Thank you so much.

232
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:26,350
Hashimottsan!

233
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:27,960
Let's go over there.

234
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:30,220
Hashimottsan? Why did you call me that?

235
00:13:30,220 --> 00:13:32,100
