236
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:33,450
It sounds like a sumo wrestler.

237
00:13:33,450 --> 00:13:35,560
With your strong slap, it's perfect.

238
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,740
I absolutely hate it.

239
00:13:37,740 --> 00:13:40,390
So you won't come with me?

240
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:43,320
I'll go with you.

241
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,930
Let's go.

242
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:47,650
I guess...

243
00:13:47,650 --> 00:13:50,470
