00:15:20,180 --> 00:15:22,480
Merry Christmas.

266
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:25,260
It was fun being able to date you.

267
00:15:25,260 --> 00:15:27,300
Thank you.

268
00:15:29,070 --> 00:15:31,050
Why...?

269
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:38,870
Ida?

270
00:15:43,420 --> 00:15:45,320
Aoki?

271
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,990
